      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That sounds a bit like corporate speak for \"people are being let go.\" I'm just trying to figure out if this is a place where I can actually build a long-term career or if the department is in a constant state of flux. Are there actually a lot of open roles because of this reorganization, or is it more about reducing the team size?",
      "beast_suffix": "",
      "targeted_response_start_logprob": 0.0
    },
