      "content": "That's a lot of hiring. But if the team is actually growing, why have so many seniors from the engineering team left in just the last few months? A few people I've talked to mentioned a pretty high turnover rate. Is the company actually expanding, or are you just trying to fill gaps left by everyone who quit?",
